title: A Joe Rogan Experience Review 181
description:
This week we review podcast 1361 Cmdr. David Fravor & Jermey Corbell and 1363 Dakota Meyer

Commander Fravor is a retired Navy Pilot who had a close encounter with a UFO and has an incredible story to tell about it. This was a 9/10 podcast for us. Definitely worth a listen.

Dakota Meyer is a retired Marine sniper who saw a lot of combat and tells a very emotional story of his time at war and his following PTSD. Below is a link to the treatment he speaks about on the podcast with Joe. If you have issues with PTSD check it out as Dakota swears by it.
